02:04:55,989 --> 02:05:00,242
I thought by distancing myself from you,
as l have done all year...

1231
02:05:00,410 --> 02:05:05,664
...he'd be less tempted, and therefore
you might be more protected.

1232
02:05:08,459 --> 02:05:11,795
The prophecy said:

1233
02:05:12,422 --> 02:05:16,383
"Neither one can live
while the other one survives."

1234
02:05:17,719 --> 02:05:23,765
It means one of us
is gonna have to kill the other, in the end.

1235
02:05:25,768 --> 02:05:27,352
Yes.

1236
02:05:27,812 --> 02:05:29,396
Why didn't you tell me?

1237
02:05:29,564 --> 02:05:33,150
For the same reason
you tried to save Sirius.

1238
02:05:33,318 --> 02:05:35,777
The same reason your friends saved you.

1239
02:05:36,613 --> 02:05:40,115
After all these years,
after all you've suffered...

1240
02:05:40,283 --> 02:05:43,202
...l didn't want to cause you
any more pain.

1241
02:05:44,662 --> 02:05:46,788
I cared too much about you.

1242
02:06:11,648 --> 02:06:13,982
How come you're not at the feast?

1243
02:06:14,150 --> 02:06:18,695
Lost all my possessions.
Apparently people have been hiding them.

1244
02:06:18,863 --> 02:06:21,949
- That's awful.
- Oh, it's all good fun.

1245
02:06:22,116 --> 02:06:25,577
But as it's the last night,
I really do need them back.

1246
02:06:25,745 --> 02:06:28,121
Do you want any help finding them?

1247
02:06:31,000 --> 02:06:34,211
I'm sorry about your godfather, Harry.

1248
02:06:41,261 --> 02:06:43,345
Are you sure you don't want
any help looking?

1249
02:06:43,513 --> 02:06:45,180
That's all right.

1250
02:06:45,348 --> 02:06:47,516
Anyway, my mum always said...

1251
02:06:47,684 --> 02:06:51,520
...the things we lose have a way
of coming back to us in the end.

1252
02:06:54,774 --> 02:06:58,026
If not always in the way we expect.

1253
02:06:59,529 --> 02:07:02,239
Think l'll just go have some pudding.

1254
02:07:37,900 --> 02:07:40,819
I've been thinking about something
Dumbledore said to me.

1255
02:07:40,987 --> 02:07:42,696
What's that?

1256
02:07:43,281 --> 02:07:46,074
That even though
we've got a fight ahead of us...

1257
02:07:46,242 --> 02:07:49,328
...we've got one thing
that Voldemort doesn't have.

1258
02:07:49,495 --> 02:07:50,996
Yeah?

1259
02:07:52,915 --> 02:07:55,250
Something worth fighting for.

